OL,3,CWoman critically injured in shark
OL,4,Cattack off Sydney's Coogee Beach
OL,6,FA woman was critically injured off a
OL,7,Fpopular Sydney beach on Saturday in
OL,8,Fthe latest in a spate of shark attacks
OL,9,Fin Australia.
OL,11,FThe woman, believed to be in her 30s,
OL,12,Fsuffered serious leg and arm injuries
OL,13,Fin the attack at 11:15 a.m. off Coogee
OL,14,FBeach, a police statement said.
OL,16,FThree spearfishing divers have been
OL,17,Fkilled by sharks off the Australian
OL,18,Fcoast since May 16, bringing the total
OL,19,Fof fatalities in the nation this year
OL,20,Fto four.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
