OL,3,CWoman critically injured in shark
OL,4,Cattack off Sydney's Coogee Beach
OL,6,FAustralia has averaged between two and
OL,7,Fthree fatal shark attacks a year since
OL,8,F2000, according to the Australian
OL,9,FShark Incident Database, a partnership
OL,10,Fof the Taronga Conservation Society
OL,11,FAustralia, Flinders University and the
OL,12,FNew South Wales state government.
OL,14,FOn Saturday, police said the victim
OL,15,Fwas attacked while swimming.
OL,16,FBystanders pulled her from the water
OL,17,Fand commenced first aid on the beach
OL,18,Fbefore paramedics arrived, the
OL,19,Fstatement said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
