OL,3,CWoman critically injured in shark
OL,4,Cattack off Sydney's Coogee Beach
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe victim was taken to a rugby field
OL,12,Fnear the beach, from where she was
OL,13,Fflown by helicopter to a hospital.
OL,14,FPolice described her condition as
OL,15,Fcritical.
OL,17,FLast Saturday, a 4.5-meter white shark
OL,18,Fkilled Daniel Turpin, 35, as he was
OL,19,Fspearfishing with family off
OL,20,FMichaelmas Island near the port city
OL,21,Fof Albany in Western Australia state.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
