OL,3,CWoman critically injured in shark
OL,4,Cattack off Sydney's Coogee Beach
OL,6,FOn May 24, 39-year-old spearfishing
OL,7,Fdiver Michael Jensz suffered fatal
OL,8,Fhead injuries in an attack on the
OL,9,FGreat Barrier Reef off Australia's
OL,10,Fnortheast coast. Bull sharks had been
OL,11,Fseen in the vicinity.
OL,13,FA week earlier, on May 16, a four-
OL,14,Fmeter white shark fatally mauled 38-
OL,15,Fyear-old spearfishing diver Steve
OL,16,FMattabonni off the coast of Perth,
OL,17,FWestern Australia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
