PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781395391
OL,3,CWoman critically injured in shark
OL,4,Cattack off Sydney's Coogee Beach
OL,6,FAustralia's other fatal shark attack
OL,7,Fthis year occurred in January, when a
OL,8,F12-year-old boy died in a hospital
OL,9,Fdays after he was mauled by a bull
OL,10,Fshark in Sydney Harbor.
OL,12,FLast year, Australia recorded five
OL,13,Ffatal shark attacks. Attacks in
OL,14,FAustralia have become more common over
OL,15,Fthe decades as the population has
OL,16,Fgrown and activities such as surfing
OL,17,Fand scuba diving have gained in
OL,18,Fpopularity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
